## Research lineage

Concept and research lineage include Jason Z. Christie’s 1998 paper
*Toward Ultimate Reality — Electronic LSD and Virtual Displays* (republished
2017) and later essays. Those writings remain under their original
publication terms; they are not re-licensed by this MIT grant unless
explicitly stated.

